sentences: Kanako Miyamoto (宮本 佳那子, Miyamoto Kanako, born November 4, 1989) is a Japanese actress, voice actress, and singer affiliated with Axlone.
Kanako Miyamoto was born on November 4, 1989 in Ibaraki Prefecture.
She was a member of the Cure Rainbows who performed Arigatō ga Ippai, the ending song of Pretty Cure All Stars DX3: Deliver the Future!
In 2013, she voiced Cure Sword (Makoto Kenzaki) in DokiDoki!

She also performed both ending songs of Kirakira PreCure a la Mode and she and Yuri Komagata, who also sang that show's opening theme song, both make cameo appearances as a pair of people auditioning for an in-universe television show alongside Himari Arisugawa/Cure Custard in the 43rd episode, which aired on 10 December 2017.
